<section id="bootiso"
         xreflabel="bootiso">
  <title>
  BootISO
  </title>

  <section>
    <title>
    Definition
    </title>

    <para>
    Allows customization of the <filename>boot.iso</filename> image
    created by <application class="software">SystemBuilder</application>. This
    image can be burned to a CD or DVD and used to begin a network installation
    on the client system.
    </para>

    <para>
    This module is a member of the <emphasis role="strong">installer</emphasis>
    module group.
    </para>
  </section>

  <section>
    <title>
    Syntax
    </title>

    <programlisting>
[&lt;bootiso [enabled=BOOLEAN]&gt;
  [&lt;boot-args [use-defaults=BOOLEAN]&gt;TEXT&lt;/boot-args&gt;]
 &lt;/bootiso&gt;]
    </programlisting>
  </section>

  <section>
    <title>
    Attributes
    </title>

    <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>
      enabled
      </term>

      <listitem>
      <para>
      See Common Attribute <emphasis><xref linkend="enabled" /></emphasis>.
      </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </section>

  <section>
    <title>
    Elements
    </title>

    <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>
      boot-args
      </term>

      <listitem>
      <para>
      Modifies the kernel boot arguments of the <filename>/isolinux/isolinux.cfg
      </filename> file within the <filename>boot.iso</filename>. The default 
      append arguments for <emphasis role="strong">bootiso</emphasis> are
      <constant>%{ks}</constant> and
      <constant>%{method}</constant>.
      See Also Common Element
      <emphasis><xref linkend="boot-args" /></emphasis>.
      </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </section>

  <section>
    <title>
    Examples
    </title>

    <informalexample>
    <programlisting>
&lt;bootiso enabled="true"&gt;
  &lt;boot-args use-defaults="false"&gt;
    keymap=us lang=en_US ip=192.168.0.222
    netmask=255.255.255.0 gateway=192.168.0.2 dns=192.168.0.7
  &lt;/boot-args&gt;
&lt;/bootiso&gt;
    </programlisting>
    </informalexample>
  </section>

  <section>
    <title>
    See Also
